    body: 'We used Top Tier on our first rental home. Carl was quick to get the work done before we rented out the home. We also a few months later used his services a second time — we had a small fire on our rental due to an old fan that failed due to age. He was out the same day of our loss and installed a new one for us. He was actually the only electrician of various I called to go out and check it the same day. I recommend his company.',
    ownerReply: "Thank you! I'll always make it out same day if possible!",
  },
  {
    author: 'Kraig Koroleski',
    date: '2026-02-21',
    body: 'Carl wired a new construction house for me — all went great, lots of good advice for first time home builders. Best advice is to walk through the build before starting to wire it and make sure you are good with the function of all the switches and outlets. How will you be using the space, how will you decorate, how far do you want to walk for switches, etc. Nice work, great dude, money well spent.',
    service: 'Installation',
    amountChip: '$2,000+',
    ownerReply:
      "Thanks Kraig! I know we went back and forth placements, and in the end I'm glad everything went above and beyond expectations!",
  },
  {
    author: 'Colten DeHaan',
    authorMeta: 'Colten DeHaan Fishing',
    date: '2026-02-14',
    body: 'Carl was great to work with! Super detailed and thoughtful of how to future proof things to avoid problems.',
    service:
      'Electrical wiring installation, Electrical outlet & switch relocation, Electrical panel repair, Electrical fixture installation',
    priceChip: 'Great price',
    amountChip: '$2,000+',
    ownerReply: "Thanks Colten! Can't wait to try out your golf simulator!",
  },
  {
    author: 'Kayley Maguire',
    date: '2026-02-14',
    body: 'We cannot recommend Carl enough! After speaking with 2 electricians before him that fell through, we were nervous. We needed an electric panel upgrade and he came over right away to give us a quote and worked with us on a date and what was needed to apply for permits. He kept us updated the entire time and was very upfront about everything. As long as he is in business we will continue to choose him for our electrical needs. Such a nice gentleman to work with — he also made sure our power was turned back on same day after dealing with the electric company instead of making us wait until Monday (this was on a Friday). Pricing was very fair and communication was excellent.',
